conversations.value: In this video, please indicate the start and end times of the equipment assembly work cycle. This cycle is from when the worker starts working at the work desk to when the worker completes the work and leaves the work desk. If there is no cycle in which work completion can be detected, identify it as an incident.
In this video, what are the start and end times of the elemental action "quality check with two check masks"? If the specified element work is not found in the video, it is identified as an incident.
In this video, detect the start and end times of the solder tank cleaning cycle. If there is no cycle that can detect the start or completion of work, identify it as an incident.

In this video, what are the start and end times of the element motion for "Remove the fixing screws of the primary and secondary nozzles, drop the solder adhering to the nozzles into the solder tank using two water pump pliers, take out the nozzle body while paying attention to leakage to the surroundings, place it on a stainless steel tray, and disassemble and clean." in the element work list? The start and end times must be output from the time of the movie itself. The element worklist file is "Solder_tank_cleaning_procedure.txt". If the specified element work is not found in the video, it is identified as an incident.
